internal.content:
---
title: Overview
---

The following are the overview of changes: 

- All three databases (Db2, Db2 Warehouse, Oracle and SQL server) are supported.
- All UI/UX (classic & work centers) will be available in Manage.
- Only WAS Liberty application server is used within MAS. 
- No significant changes in the EAM data model.
- Red Hat OpenShift Deployment.
